ISLAMABAD, Nov 22 (APP):The Islamabad Capital Territory (ICT) Police on Wednesday detained 13 illegal foreigners during its operation in the limits of Bani Gala, Sabzi Mandi, and Shams Colony police stations.
The detainees were subsequently handed over to the ICT administration for repatriation to their native countries.
